section.def:
Modified Regulations (《經變通規例》) means the Road Traffic (Registration and
            Licensing of Vehicles) Regulations (Cap. 374 sub. leg. E),
            as modified by Part IV of Schedule 2 to the Bylaw;

prohibited zone permit (禁區許可證) means a relevant permit issued by the Authority
            with the approval of the Commissioner for the purposes of section 50(1)(a) of
            the Modified Regulations;
